Monitoring
==========
`Glances`_ is a good tool for monitoring the status of docker instances.
It can be installed like this:

.. code-block:: bash

   curl -L http://bit.ly/glances | /bin/bash

and run like this

.. code-block:: bash

   sudo glances


.. _`Glances`: https://nicolargo.github.io/glances


